==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Regerminate
<hw>Re*ger"mi*nate</hw> <pr>(r?*j?r"m?*n?t)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos>
<ety>[Pref. <ets>re-</ets> + <ets>germinate</ets>: cf. L.
<ets>regerminare</ets>.]</ety> <def>To germinate again.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Perennial plants <qex>regerminate</qex> several years
successively.</q> <rj><qau>J. Lee.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Regermination</ent>⟦br⟧
